Sandra Gould https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sandra_Gould 0 Sandra Gould (July 23, 1916 – July 20, 1999) was an American actress, perhaps best known for her role as Gladys Kravitz on the sitcom Bewitched. Gould was the second actress to portray the role, debuting in the third season.
